{"tid":2207191,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"狗仔係咁咬人手腳","createTime":"2020-09-18T04:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T04:29:41.000Z","uid":89371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bba6a16cc0159033ef305ae92522bead9de10669","tid":2207191,"uid":89371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:15:27.000Z","msg":"狗仔而家6個月，嚟左屋企個幾星期<br />\n一玩到癲就會咬人手腳，俾玩具佢咬佢都好似係鍾意咬人手腳多啲<br />\n有冇咩方法可以解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884046a75172561324b6e7c7f5c81a1a0c3d2bad","tid":2207191,"uid":78995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:29:16.000Z","msg":"我比隻手掌佢，特登引佢咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當佢一咬個時，我就用手指頂到最入（近佢喉嚨）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢咬兩下後就會想作嘔，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重覆幾次之後，狗狗對我隻手冇晒興趣了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b3daab15a0aadb340a68a5e153755d836a80704","tid":2207191,"uid":293296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:29:41.000Z","msg":"大個咗就唔咬"}]}